---
title: Panko Fried Chicken Breasts with Spiced Fries and Gravy
description: There is nothing better than that first bite of crispy, crunchy fried chicken! Tonight we are going all out, pairing it with BBQ spiced fries, gravy and creamy, dreamy coleslaw!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/panko-fried-chicken-breasts-dcdf0a5c.jpg
